[SN]TITLE[SN]
Woman dies in crash on A40 near Llanspyddid

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman has died and another has been taken to hospital following a two-vehicle crash in Powys.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Dyfed-Powys Police was called to the A40 near Llanspyddid, near Brecon, at 07:35 GMT on Friday.
The woman who was killed was 58 and a 21-year-old remains in hospital.
Police are investigating the cause of the crash and the road has since reopened.
